column1: 1920 Nov 11th Gauge moved about 150 yds SW to lower level
Exact location unknown but this NGR matches distance and altitude
1925 Row of tall elms 20yrds E Felled in Feb 1927
1929 Oct 1st Gauge moved 6ft E to new recommended position
1944 Observer states gauge is sound and site unaltered
1948 Oct Gauge terminated on death of observer
